But, if we studied the situation in detail, the things are more complicated.
According to the Agreement of Copenhagen, the money must be "new and additional" to guarantee that a complementary effort is realized, without harming to the official aid to the development.
Unfortunately, one has not reached an agreement exceeds what means "new and additional."
